messages.content: Venor - No. she's.. She doesn't know at this point. - stumbles outside. "Are you okay?" She sounds really worried. "Lamia?"
*mm?*
"This is... weird." Venor anxiously taps her hands together. "Are you alright?"
*I think?*
"Do you know-" *What happened?* Venor switches to just thinking.
*Not really but it's probably the work of a stand*
*...Yeah. Should we... go find whichever stand did this?* Venor concentrates and opens two eyes on the palms of her hands.
*Maybe...*
*Okay, wait.* Venor shakes their.. her legs out. *Let's just... calm down first.* She sounds like she's saying that to herself more than anyone.
Venor takes a few reassuring breaths and nods. "Okay. I'm... calmer now."
"That's good."
//sorry hdjfndn
((you cool 👍 ))
"So.. We should probably work as a team to find this stand." Venor takes the initiative again.
"Have our stands fused?"
"I don't know... Careless Whisper!" The stand shimmers into view. "Doesn't look like it. Maybe we have to be more in sync?"
"Try what that ASSHOLE Polaris does and call it 'Careless Whisper: The World'!"
"Okay." Venor desummons her stand. "Careless Whisper: The World!" It looks the same.
Lamia was also concentrating. "it'd be cool if our stands were fused."
"Again. I think we have to be more in sync."
"Ok." He tried
Venor slows her thoughts... and there. Venandi. That's definitely what they're calling themself.
"Venandi?"
"Damn it Lamia. We were there for a second." Venor rolls her eyes. "Apparently fused us likes to call themself Venandi."
"Ok, whatever Vegito wants."
"V... I feel offended for someone who's not even quite me."
Lamia chuckles
"I think... I think they're even more of a bastard than us." Venor clutches at the receding feeling of being Venandi. "How is that even *possible*?!"
"Two bastards combined"

"You wanna go back to being them? Maybe ultimate bastard can track down whoever fused us." Venor grins.

Black Orchid has been hiding in a bush, listening in to the conversation, and she grins. This should be interesting.
"Sure."
Venor tries to slow down her thoughts again. *Hm.*
Lamia does the same
Venandi is back, and they hope to dear god Lamia doesn't get distracted again. They rather like being around, thank you very much.
Lamia is focused on finding whoever fused him with Venor and kicking their ass
Black Orchid makes a rustling sound and freezes. "Aw fuck."
*hmmmm*

Venandi tilts their head and bounds over. Very much a bastard.

"Oi, you asshole better shove off right now." Black Orchid yells right back at them.

Venandi cracks their knuckles. 
*Always wanted to do that!*

Black Orchid steps back.

Venandi folds their other pair of arms loosely. "Who're you?"
"You better start spitting some answers in the next second."

"I have no idea what you want to know, you assholes." Black Orchid folds her arms in return.

"Oh really?" Venandi replies.
"were you not nosing in on our conversation just now?"

"...How would you know that?" Black Orchid suddenly looks shifty.

"She really isn't hard to read." Venandi muses. "How about you tell us everything now?" They put their first pair of arms on their knees. "Or would you like the punching first?"
Some sort...of stand fusion begins to manifest

Black Orchid loses some of her assholish demeanor. "What the fuck is that."

"Dunno. Looks like our stands fused as well." Venandi fistbumps the stand. "Not bad."
"Careless World."

"Oh, that is an *excellent* name. *Thank* you, me." Venandi grins. "You wanna try this out, Careless World?" 

Black Orchid makes a run for it.
Caeli is flying around here looking for black orchid.
Black Orchid is sitting on a tree branch. SHe looks in rough shape.
He notices her and flies to her. "Hi there!"
Black Orchid rolls her eyes and flips her off. Rude.
Caeli is >:/ "Hey! What did I do to you?"
"You *existed.* Today's been fucking bad enough already. I got sucked into this *stupid dumb as fuck void* and accidentally made a *double bastard* and it's fucking awful."
"The void is pretty cool, thank you very much! Your ability is super cool!"
"I could do without it, it's fucking stupid, and I hate this fucking stupid ass void." Black Orchid kicks her tree branch.
"How about I show you around so you can see how cool this place is?"
"No. Fuck you."
((lmao
((pff))
>:( "what the hell is your deal?! Why are you so rude?!"
Black Orchid glares at him and flips him off again.
"Listen, all I wanna do is to be able to fuse with this one mun I really really like!"
"I'm not your fucking fuse stand. Shoo before I fuse you with this tree."
"Alright, fine! Geez, sorry for bothering you."
Black Orchid throws a ball of light at him. He'll fuse with the next mun who he gets close to.
He flies off to find Helio, very pissed off at his perceived failure.
